#. module: sports_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:sports_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"a) The Club has a bar where players can grab something to eat between games "
"or have a beer.<br/>\n"
"            It can be accessed in\n"
"            <strong>\n"
"                <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Point of Sales &gt; Bar </"
"font><font class=\"text-black\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">and "
"contains some basic products.</span></font>\n"
"            </strong>\n"
"            <br/>\n"
"            Customers can pay by through different means, including by "
"adding the note to their account."
msgstr ""
"a) Clubul are un bar unde jucătorii pot lua ceva de mâncare între meciuri "
"sau pot bea o bere.<br/>\n"
"            Acesta poate fi accesat din\n"
"            <strong>\n"
"                <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Punct de vânzare &gt; Bar </"
"font><font class=\"text-black\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">și "
"conține câteva produse de bază.</span></font>\n"
"            </strong>\n"
"            <br/>\n"
"            Clienții pot plăti prin diferite metode, inclusiv prin adăugarea "
"notei pe contul lor."

#. module: sports_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:sports_club.homepage
